itemgroup.item:
p{: style='text-align:left'}
p{: style='text-align:right'}
p{: style='text-align:center'}
p{: style='text-align:justify'}

XWiki 1.0 syntax:

{image:img.png}
{image:img.png|document=Space.Page} 
{image:img.png|width=25|height=25}
http://some/url/img.png 

XWiki 2.0 syntax:

image:img.png
image:Space.Page@img.png
[[image:img.png||width="25" height="25"]]
image:http://some/url/img.png

//italics//
also supported "old" style
''2 quotes are italic''

#left(){text align is left}
#right(){text align is right}
#center(){text align is center}

@title Some Title
@subtitle Some Subtitle
@subsubtitle Some Subsubtitle

{{p|align:left|text of paragraph}}
{{p|align:center|text of paragraph}}
{{p|align:right|text of paragraph}}
